      <scopecontent id="aspace_162a2be9930b5962ca877e587b70ed31">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, subject files, and related materials concerning Yale Corporation affairs, scholarships and prizes, honorary degrees, and other activities administered by the secretary's office during the tenure of Franklin B. Dexter, 1869-1899.</p>  
